<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Reset Your Password</title>
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f7fa; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; }
    .header { background-color: #e8431a; padding: 32px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; }
    .body { padding: 40px; color: #333333; line-height: 1.6; }
    .body h2 { margin-top: 0; color: #333333; font-size: 20px; }
    .body p { margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 15px; }
    .cta { display: inline-block; background-color: #e8431a; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 32px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; margin: 8px 0 24px; }
    .link-fallback { word-break: break-all; color: #1a73e8; font-size: 13px; }
    .warning { background-color: #fff8e1; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 12px 16px; margin: 16px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #665500; }
    .footer { background-color: #f4f7fa; padding: 24px 40px; text-align: center; color: #888888; font-size: 13px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Password Reset Request</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <h2>Hi {{name}},</h2>
      <p>We received a request to reset the password for your account. Click the button below to choose a new password. This link will expire in {{expiresIn}}.</p>
      <p style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="cta">Reset Password</a>
      </p>
      <p>If the button does not work, copy and paste the following URL into your browser:</p>
      <p class="link-fallback">{{resetUrl}}</p>
      <div class="warning">
        If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email or contact support if you believe your account has been compromised.
      </div>
      <p>Best regards,<br />The {{appName}} Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{year}} {{appName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
